{"tid":1776063,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「大核彈」大波嬅無去過北京，而係去左新疆。","createTime":"2019-12-09T09:12:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-09T10:37:19.000Z","uid":220066,"like":8,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"2743d86ea89d767189bddd632a8c3ccd81755df6","tid":1776063,"uid":220066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T09:12:26.000Z","msg":"自從佢突然番香港之後<br />\n發現佢回應完記者提問之後<br />\n都係雙目無神，無曬中氣<br />\n完全受到壓逼先會番來香港<br />\n<br />\n睇番佢會見記者期間<br />\n眼神都係好驚荒<br />\n完全同佢去英國之前同之後出現好大比<br />\n<br />\n大波嬅係英國比中共捉左去新彊<br />\n接受一連串既洗腦教育同埋酷刑對待<br />\n至於佢講係北京番來香港，呢個係真既<br />\n但係佢係由新彊去北京再轉機番落來香港<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ddTWLLm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FddTWLLm.png&h=ea2e07bf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xosHGjd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxosHGjd.png&h=06430cd2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n至於你地信唔信就由你地去判斷啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa70c7ee986af9d73499cc531654994d2b440a57","tid":1776063,"uid":1971,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T09:20:20.000Z","msg":"唔好哄我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9b3b34a61f2f84099d73fd965bc1249236add7b","tid":1776063,"uid":61280,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T09:23:57.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">佢返黎個西樣，似嘆完水地獄加十八羅漢陣返黎就真囉！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"aef9fbbb47aac053737c34579d73d925e152e875","tid":1776063,"uid":51057,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T09:29:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosa